      <section id="id4296088">
        <title>STARTING YOUR BUSINESS</title>
        <para id="id5997783">A business starts with an idea. </para>
        <para id="id1171525850377">Are you going to . . .</para>
        <list id="id4403277" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
          <item>Buy or sell?</item>
          <item>Provide a service?</item>
          <item>Produce and market your own product?</item>
          <item>Put your skills and talent to work?</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id8151885">Consider these four points carefully. List your ideas.</para>
        <para id="id8888903">You have three minutes to work on your own.</para>
      </section>
