      <section id="id4494623">
        <title>[LO 4.1.3]</title>
        <para id="id1171529469768">Think carefully about the kind of business you intend starting.</para>
        <para id="id1171527152124">ARE YOU GOING TO . . . </para>
        <para id="id1171521820389">1. buy and sell?</para>
        <para id="id8020904">2. produce and market your own product?</para>
        <para id="id4889886">3. provide a service?</para>
        <para id="id1171520425901">4. put your talents and skills to work?</para>
        <para id="id2089621">What business did you decide on? </para>
        <para id="id3736181">Now draw up your <emphasis effect="bold">own business plan </emphasis>for your business <emphasis effect="italics">in rough</emphasis>. </para>
        <para id="id3082927">You must remember to focus on the four business basics:</para>
