        <para id="id1171522577312">You now need to compile <emphasis effect="italics">a final business plan</emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">, </emphasis>using the rough draft as a guide. </para>
        <para id="id1171528192294">Why a business plan is vital</para>
        <para id="id1171530416922">If you need to borrow money to get started, you will be asked to present your business plan. </para>
        <para id="id1171520162259">It will also keep you focused on your goals. </para>
        <para id="id7276482">Business success needs a combination of imagination and initiative, hard work and discipline. Reveal these features in your business plan.</para>
        <para id="id1171528202510">Take note before you start:</para>
        <para id="id1171526088156">This assignment will be <emphasis effect="italics">assessed</emphasis> by your educator. </para>
        <para id="id1171520462042">The task consists of <emphasis effect="bold">FOUR</emphasis> sections with a separate <emphasis effect="italics">CHECKLIST</emphasis><emphasis effect="italics"/><emphasis effect="italics"/>for each.</para>
        <para id="id3637871">Do each section on a separate page. </para>
        <para id="id3777539">Bind the pages in a file, folder or plastic sleeve before handing the project in.</para>
        <para id="id3453657">Your rough work must also be handed in.</para>
